## Implementations

### Duhamel's Integral — `Duhamel_Integral_SDOF.xlsx`
Excel workbook with four load cases. Change the blue input cells (mass, stiffness, damping) and the charts update automatically.

| Sheet | Load |
|---|---|
| Free Vibration | Initial displacement / velocity |
| Harmonic | F₀·sin(ωt) — try setting ω = ωₙ to see resonance |
| Impact | Short rectangular pulse |
| Ground Motion | Seismic base acceleration |

