### Frequency Domain Solver — `Frequency_Domain_Response.html`
Open in any browser. Paste a discrete accelerogram, adjust system parameters, and the tool computes the SDOF response via FFT — the approach used when the load is recorded data rather than an analytical function.

Shows: input signal → frequency spectrum → transfer function → displacement response.

